  "name": "Polyglot Cup (OpenAI)",
  "description": "dropper -> parse -> audio_transcribe -> question -> prompt -> llm_openai -> response_answers. OpenAI variant of Polyglot Cup: parallel-transcribe short World Cup fan clips in their native language, then translate + tag the moment to English. Swap target for the live llm_anthropic -> llm_openai closer.",
